OL,5, Four women have been selected to run   
OL,6, the world's most remote post office and
OL,7, count penguins in Antarctica.          
OL,9,FClare Ballantyne, Mairi Hilton, Natalie
OL,10,FCorbett and Lucy Bruzzone beat a record
OL,11,Fnumber of applicants to become the team
OL,12,Fresponsible for managing historic site 
OL,13,FPort Lockroy, on Goudier Island.       
OL,15,FThe team will travel 9,000 miles from  
OL,16,Fthe UK to reopen the bay for the first 
OL,17,Ftime since the coronavirus pandemic.   
OL,19,FThey will spend five months without    
OL,20,Frunning water or a flushing toilet.    
